'''Dianoga cheese''' was a type of [[Cheese/Legends|cheese]], similar in color to the skin of a [[Skup/Legends|Sionian Skup]]. Its connection with the animal [[Species/Legends|species]] known as the [[Dianoga/Legends|dianoga]] is unknown.

